{"tid":1041555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】【真係無地？】政府一邊搶地起豪宅，一邊天價買貴舖","createTime":"2019-03-01T01:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T01:38:20.000Z","uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b8b58021273157477b7235bdea9a936e45dd63","tid":1041555,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2204342489661812/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2204342489661812%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=582ed695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2204342489661812/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n琴日我哋踢爆劏房波撥200億公帑掃貨、用天價買60個物業話做社福設施(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NAViXL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NAViXL&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=54951ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NAViXL</a>) ，今日議員就喺立法會齊齊質問佢係咪想托市益財團。結果劏房波惱羞成怒，係咁話議員「顛倒是非，混淆視聽」（但又駁唔到），覺得60歲係中年嗰個羅致光仲話討論選址無意思，係因為社福用地需求好殷切先會咁做，講好受委屈慘慘豬咁。<br />\n<br />\n但另一邊廂，政府今日最新公佈嘅賣地表當中，咪正正有三塊地（葵涌荔崗街、九龍旺角新填地街及上海街、九龍旺角豉油街與上海街交界）以前係劃咗做社福用途囉！三塊地夾埋逾50,000呎，早就可以用來起安老院、長者中心，咁心繫長者嘅話，點解又拎嚟賣俾發展商賺錢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">事實上，政府自2013年至今，已總共將25塊可作社福用途嘅「政府、機構或社區」（G/IC）用地改劃做私營房屋，哩批土地面積合共成27公頃。</span>以現時一間位於沙田嘅津助院舍（註）為例，佔地0.197公頃已提供到204個宿位，每位平均樓面達28.2平方米，可算十分寬敞。就算用哩個標準，1公頃都可以起到1,035個宿位，27公頃就有<span style=\"color: gold;\">27,945個</span>喇！如果哩批社福用地過去幾年有用來起院舍，今日已經可以一炮過清晒現時輪候緊安老院舍嘅活躍個案。<br />\n<br />\n辦法總比藉口多。政府有心做嘅話，根本大把地方可以拎嚟起社福設施。除咗上述被搶去起私樓豪宅嘅社福地外，我哋上年發佈嘅《隱藏選項：香港臨時使用及閒置官地研究》亦都發掘到，<span style=\"color: gold;\">市區內現時有多達90公頃、已劃為G/IC用途但未有長遠發展計劃嘅官地，可以直接拎嚟起社福設施，但依家只用嚟泊車、甚至喺度養野草、曬太陽</span>，就係唔起社福設施益老友記。<br />\n<br />\n此外，而家起緊嘅公共屋邨同市區重建項目，都可以喺低層預留空間做社福設施；就算要發展私人屋苑，亦都可喺賣地條款規定發展商須興建特定面積嘅社福設施，好似上年售出嘅啟德「地王」第1F區1號住宅地皮一早就做緊，但政府就唔願意承諾將哩種方式定為恆常政策。咁多方法唔做，依家就喺度<span style=\"color: gold;\">慷公帑之慨，豪花公帑掃舖位</span>，背後目的真係耐人尋味！<br />\n<br />\n註： 參考沙田群芳念慈護老院，該處佔地0.197公頃，為七層建築，住用樓面面積5,747平方米，提供204個宿位。"},{"pid":"2b0a46550b788de37440a6ac3ebb9e78e0adfa44","tid":1041555,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"🎈《隱藏選項》報告: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/missingoption2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fmissingoption2018&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=64e21f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/missingoption2018</a><br />\n🌎《隱藏選項》地圖: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/missingoption_map\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fmissingoption_map&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=bda3e1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/missingoption_map</a><br />\n<br />\n月捐撐本研 一齊踢爆官商謊言<br />\n💪了解更多: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=041a2d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/about-us</a><br />\n💰支持我們: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/support-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=c379b672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/support-us</a>"},{"pid":"8616ff59f8ee417da30fff74ddfb5594371c304f","tid":1041555,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"唉, 要搵人買蝕本貨所以政府要出手了!"},{"pid":"2e02a52feb39fa69d7d6643d2df40e52291791b3","tid":1041555,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"冚家鏟 5千億外匯基金組合 就嚟俾老董系控制 玩地產玩一帶一路 都冇人講！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1041557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1041557</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d56b0f33b2bbd0d6774382251b6a41ab13826e7","tid":1041555,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ8CvA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ8CvA2.jpg&h=df60025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吹咩？"},{"pid":"bf76a1f24e2b2b311228e9b208c778f47f1e909e","tid":1041555,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2732358fd3445200235f6b2e42241911515525a0","tid":1041555,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}